- [Deployment Guide](docs/DEPLOYMENT_GUIDE.md)
- [V31 Model Training Walkthrough](docs/reports/finbert_v31_transformer_walkthrough.md)
- [Project Plans](docs/plans/)

## 🏗️ Architecture
The system consists of three main microservices:
1. **Frontend**: React + Vite dashboard.
2. **Gateway**: Node.js/Express API gateway.
3. **AI Service**: Python/Flask service running the FinBERT model.

